        "liquid_3BF6VF": {
          "type": "liquid",
          "settings": {
            "liquid": "<div style=\"position: relative; overflow: hidden; margin: 20px 0;\">\n\n  <!-- SLIDES WRAPPER -->\n  <div id=\"review-track\" style=\"display: flex; transition: transform 0.4s ease; will-change: transform;\">\n\n    <!-- AVIS 1 -->\n    <div style=\"min-width: 100%; background: #f3f4f6; border-radius: 12px; padding: 20px; box-sizing: border-box;\">\n      <div style=\"display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 10px; margin-bottom: 12px;\">\n        <img src=\"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0814/7897/5709/files/Screenshot_2026-02-06_at_8.56.23_AM_430x.png?v=1773259151\" \n          style=\"width: 52px; height: 52px; border-radius: 50%; object-fit: cover;\" />\n        <div>\n          <p style=\"margin: 0; font-weight: 700; font-size: 14px; color: #111;\">Klaus Berger</p>\n          <span style=\"color: #f59e0b; font-size: 18px;\">★★★★★</span>\n        </div>\n      </div>\n      <p style=\"margin: 0; font-size: 14px; line-height: 1.7; color: #111;\">\n        Ich hatte Bedenken wegen meines empfindlichen Magens — ich dachte, das würde mir Sodbrennen bereiten. Nach zwei Monaten: absolut nichts. Kein Reflux, keine Magenprobleme. Ich hätte es früher probieren sollen.\n      </p>\n    </div>\n\n    <!-- AVIS 2 -->\n    <div style=\"min-width: 100%; background: #f3f4f6; border-radius: 12px; padding: 20px; box-sizing: border-box;\">\n      <div style=\"display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 10px; margin-bottom: 12px;\">\n        <img src=\"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0814/7897/5709/files/2c540bcf-9536-4b6f-bb27-e8eed0265cfc_430x.png?v=1773259153\" \n          style=\"width: 52px; height: 52px; border-radius: 50%; object-fit: cover;\" />\n        <div>\n          <p style=\"margin: 0; font-weight: 700; font-size: 14px; color: #111;\">Thomas Müller</p>\n          <span style=\"color: #f59e0b; font-size: 18px;\">★★★★★</span>\n        </div>\n      </div>\n      <p style=\"margin: 0; font-size: 14px; line-height: 1.7; color: #111;\">\n        Ich bin Diabetiker seit 9 Jahren und mein Arzt sagte mir, schlechte Durchblutung sei „normal\". Seit 6 Wochen Capsaicin Power spüre ich einen echten Unterschied — wärmere Hände, mehr Energie, und das Kribbeln in den Beinen ist fast verschwunden.\n      </p>\n    </div>\n\n    <!-- AVIS 3 -->\n    <div style=\"min-width: 100%; background: #f3f4f6; border-radius: 12px; padding: 20px; box-sizing: border-box;\">\n      <div style=\"display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 10px; margin-bottom: 12px;\">\n        <img src=\"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0814/7897/5709/files/Screenshot_2026-02-06_at_8.55.50_AM_430x.png?v=1773259150\" \n          style=\"width: 52px; height: 52px; border-radius: 50%; object-fit: cover;\" />\n        <div>\n          <p style=\"margin: 0; font-weight: 700; font-size: 14px; color: #111;\">Werner Schmidt</p>\n          <span style=\"color: #f59e0b; font-size: 18px;\">★★★★★</span>\n        </div>\n      </div>\n      <p style=\"margin: 0; font-size: 14px; line-height: 1.7; color: #111;\">\n        Ich war 6 Monate lang skeptisch. Ashwagandha, Zink, Maca — alles probiert, nichts hat funktioniert. Ein Freund hat mir Capsaicin Power empfohlen. Nach 3 Wochen merkte ich, dass mein Blutdruck stabiler wurde. Jetzt bin ich beim zweiten Beutel.\n      </p>\n    </div>\n\n  </div>\n\n  <!-- NAVIGATION -->\n  <div style=\"display: flex; justify-content: center; align-items: center; gap: 20px; margin-top: 14px;\">\n    <button onclick=\"reviewSlide(-1)\" style=\"background: none; border: 1px solid #d1d5db; border-radius: 50%; width: 36px; height: 36px; font-size: 16px; cursor: pointer; color: #374151;\">‹</button>\n    <div id=\"review-dots\" style=\"display: flex; gap: 6px;\">\n      <span onclick=\"reviewGoTo(0)\" style=\"width: 8px; height: 8px; border-radius: 50%; background: #cb4b45; cursor: pointer; display: block;\"></span>\n      <span onclick=\"reviewGoTo(1)\" style=\"width: 8px; height: 8px; border-radius: 50%; background: #d1d5db; cursor: pointer; display: block;\"></span>\n      <span onclick=\"reviewGoTo(2)\" style=\"width: 8px; height: 8px; border-radius: 50%; background: #d1d5db; cursor: pointer; display: block;\"></span>\n    </div>\n    <button onclick=\"reviewSlide(1)\" style=\"background: none; border: 1px solid #d1d5db; border-radius: 50%; width: 36px; height: 36px; font-size: 16px; cursor: pointer; color: #374151;\">›</button>\n  </div>\n\n</div>\n\n<script>\n  var reviewCurrent = 0;\n  var reviewTotal = 3;\n\n  function reviewGoTo(index) {\n    reviewCurrent = index;\n    document.getElementById('review-track').style.transform = 'translateX(-' + (reviewCurrent * 100) + '%)';\n    var dots = document.getElementById('review-dots').children;\n    for (var i = 0; i < dots.length; i++) {\n      dots[i].style.background = i === reviewCurrent ? '#cb4b45' : '#d1d5db';\n    }\n  }\n\n  function reviewSlide(dir) {\n    reviewCurrent = (reviewCurrent + dir + reviewTotal) % reviewTotal;\n    reviewGoTo(reviewCurrent);\n  }\n</script>"
          }
        },
        "liquid_Q3DD9i": {
          "type": "liquid",
          "settings": {
            "liquid": "<div style=\"margin: 20px 0; border-top: 1px solid #e5e7eb;\">\n\n  <!-- FAQ 1 -->\n  <div style=\"border-bottom: 1px solid #e5e7eb;\">\n    <button onclick=\"toggleFaq(this)\" style=\"width: 100%; display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: space-between; padding: 14px 0; background: none; border: none; cursor: pointer; text-align: left;\">\n      <div style=\"display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 10px;\">\n        <svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"18\" height=\"18\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"#cb4b45\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\"><polyline points=\"9 11 12 14 22 4\"/><path d=\"M21 12v7a2 2 0 0 1-2 2H5a2 2 0 0 1-2-2V5a2 2 0 0 1 2-2h11\"/></svg>\n        <span style=\"font-size: 14px; font-weight: 700; color: #111;\">Wann sehe ich erste Ergebnisse?</span>\n      </div>\n      <svg class=\"faq-arrow\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"16\" height=\"16\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"#6b7280\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\"><polyline points=\"6 9 12 15 18 9\"/></svg>\n    </button>\n    <div class=\"faq-answer\" style=\"display: none; padding: 0 0 14px 28px;\">\n      <p style=\"margin: 0; font-size: 13px; color: #374151; line-height: 1.6;\">Die meisten Kunden spüren nach 2–4 Wochen eine verbesserte Durchblutung und mehr Energie. Für optimale Ergebnisse empfehlen wir eine Einnahme über mindestens 60 Tage.</p>\n    </div>\n  </div>\n\n  <!-- FAQ 2 -->\n  <div style=\"border-bottom: 1px solid #e5e7eb;\">\n    <button onclick=\"toggleFaq(this)\" style=\"width: 100%; display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: space-between; padding: 14px 0; background: none; border: none; cursor: pointer; text-align: left;\">\n      <div style=\"display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 10px;\">\n        <svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"18\" height=\"18\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"#cb4b45\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\"><polyline points=\"9 11 12 14 22 4\"/><path d=\"M21 12v7a2 2 0 0 1-2 2H5a2 2 0 0 1-2-2V5a2 2 0 0 1 2-2h11\"/></svg>\n        <span style=\"font-size: 14px; font-weight: 700; color: #111;\">Wie nehme ich es ein?</span>\n      </div>\n      <svg class=\"faq-arrow\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"16\" height=\"16\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"#6b7280\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\"><polyline points=\"6 9 12 15 18 9\"/></svg>\n    </button>\n    <div class=\"faq-answer\" style=\"display: none; padding: 0 0 14px 28px;\">\n      <p style=\"margin: 0; font-size: 13px; color: #374151; line-height: 1.6;\">Täglich 3–4 Softgels mit einem großen Glas Wasser einnehmen, vorzugsweise zu einer Mahlzeit. Die Softgel-Form wurde speziell entwickelt, um Magenprobleme zu vermeiden.</p>\n    </div>\n  </div>\n\n  <!-- FAQ 3 -->\n  <div style=\"border-bottom: 1px solid #e5e7eb;\">\n    <button onclick=\"toggleFaq(this)\" style=\"width: 100%; display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: space-between; padding: 14px 0; background: none; border: none; cursor: pointer; text-align: left;\">\n      <div style=\"display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 10px;\">\n        <svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"18\" height=\"18\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"#cb4b45\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\"><polyline points=\"9 11 12 14 22 4\"/><path d=\"M21 12v7a2 2 0 0 1-2 2H5a2 2 0 0 1-2-2V5a2 2 0 0 1 2-2h11\"/></svg>\n        <span style=\"font-size: 14px; font-weight: 700; color: #111;\">Verursacht es Sodbrennen?</span>\n      </div>\n      <svg class=\"faq-arrow\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"16\" height=\"16\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"#6b7280\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\"><polyline points=\"6 9 12 15 18 9\"/></svg>\n    </button>\n    <div class=\"faq-answer\" style=\"display: none; padding: 0 0 14px 28px;\">\n      <p style=\"margin: 0; font-size: 13px; color: #374151; line-height: 1.6;\">Nein. Anders als herkömmliche Cayennepfeffer-Kapseln ist Capsaicin Power in magenschonender Softgel-Form erhältlich und enthält Kurkuma, das Sodbrennen und Reflux aktiv verhindert.</p>\n    </div>\n  </div>\n\n  <!-- FAQ 4 -->\n  <div style=\"border-bottom: 1px solid #e5e7eb;\">\n    <button onclick=\"toggleFaq(this)\" style=\"width: 100%; display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: space-between; padding: 14px 0; background: none; border: none; cursor: pointer; text-align: left;\">\n      <div style=\"display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 10px;\">\n        <svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"18\" height=\"18\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"#cb4b45\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\"><polyline points=\"9 11 12 14 22 4\"/><path d=\"M21 12v7a2 2 0 0 1-2 2H5a2 2 0 0 1-2-2V5a2 2 0 0 1 2-2h11\"/></svg>\n        <span style=\"font-size: 14px; font-weight: 700; color: #111;\">60-Tage Geld-zurück-Garantie</span>\n      </div>\n      <svg class=\"faq-arrow\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"16\" height=\"16\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"#6b7280\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\"><polyline points=\"6 9 12 15 18 9\"/></svg>\n    </button>\n    <div class=\"faq-answer\" style=\"display: none; padding: 0 0 14px 28px;\">\n      <p style=\"margin: 0; font-size: 13px; color: #374151; line-height: 1.6;\">Wenn Sie innerhalb von 60 Tagen nicht zufrieden sind, erstatten wir Ihnen den vollen Kaufpreis — ohne Fragen. Einfach eine E-Mail an support@nelorya.com schicken.</p>\n    </div>\n  </div>\n\n  <!-- FAQ 5 -->\n  <div style=\"border-bottom: 1px solid #e5e7eb;\">\n    <button onclick=\"toggleFaq(this)\" style=\"width: 100%; display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: space-between; padding: 14px 0; background: none; border: none; cursor: pointer; text-align: left;\">\n      <div style=\"display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 10px;\">\n        <svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"18\" height=\"18\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"#cb4b45\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\"><polyline points=\"9 11 12 14 22 4\"/><path d=\"M21 12v7a2 2 0 0 1-2 2H5a2 2 0 0 1-2-2V5a2 2 0 0 1 2-2h11\"/></svg>\n        <span style=\"font-size: 14px; font-weight: 700; color: #111;\">Versand & Lieferung</span>\n      </div>\n      <svg class=\"faq-arrow\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"16\" height=\"16\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"#6b7280\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\"><polyline points=\"6 9 12 15 18 9\"/></svg>\n    </button>\n    <div class=\"faq-answer\" style=\"display: none; padding: 0 0 14px 28px;\">\n      <p style=\"margin: 0; font-size: 13px; color: #374151; line-height: 1.6;\">Versand innerhalb von 24 Stunden. Lieferung nach Deutschland in 7–12 Werktagen. Kostenloser Versand ab dem ersten Beutel.</p>\n    </div>\n  </div>\n\n</div>\n\n<script>\n  function toggleFaq(btn) {\n    var answer = btn.nextElementSibling;\n    var arrow = btn.querySelector('.faq-arrow');\n    var isOpen = answer.style.display === 'block';\n    answer.style.display = isOpen ? 'none' : 'block';\n    arrow.style.transform = isOpen ? 'rotate(0deg)' : 'rotate(180deg)';\n    arrow.style.transition = 'transform 0.2s ease';\n  }\n</script>"
